title: Estadio Roberto Suazo Córdova
text: Estadio Roberto Suazo Córdova is a multi-use <a href="stadium">stadium</a> in <a href="La%20Paz%2C%20Honduras">La Paz</a>, <a href="Honduras">Honduras</a>. It is currently used mostly for <a href="Association%20football">football</a> matches and is the home of <a href="Municipal%20Pace%C3%B1o">Municipal Paceño</a>. The stadium holds 25,000 people.
